Hughes Satellite Systems Corporation: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 29, 2017 12:49 AM ET
Diversified Telecommunication Services

Company Overview of Hughes Satellite Systems Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hughes Satellite Systems Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, provides satellite service operations, video delivery solutions, and broadband satellite technologies and services for homes and offices in the United States. It operates through two segments, Hughes and EchoStar Satellite Services. The Hughes segment offers satellite broadband Internet access, broadband services, managed services, and communication solutions to the domestic, international, enterprise, and government customers. The EchoStar Satellite Services segment provides satellite services on a full-time and occasional-use basis through its owned and leased in-orbit satellites primarily to DISH Network Corporation and...
Hughes Satellite Systems Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, provides satellite service operations, video delivery solutions, and broadband satellite technologies and services for homes and offices in the United States. It operates through two segments, Hughes and EchoStar Satellite Services. The Hughes segment offers satellite broadband Internet access, broadband services, managed services, and communication solutions to the domestic, international, enterprise, and government customers. The EchoStar Satellite Services segment provides satellite services on a full-time and occasional-use basis through its owned and leased in-orbit satellites primarily to DISH Network Corporation and to Dish Mexico and S. de R.L. de C.V., as well as to the United States government service providers, Internet service providers, broadcast news organizations, programmers, and private enterprise customers. The company also delivers network technologies, managed services, and solutions for enterprises and government customers. The company was formerly known as EH Holding Corporation and changed its name to Hughes Satellite Systems Corporation in October 2011. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Englewood, Colorado. Hughes Satellite Systems Corporation is a subsidiary of EchoStar Corporation.
Detailed Description


100 Inverness Terrace EastEnglewood, CO 80112United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 303-706-4000








